                "invention-title": [
                    "Perm agent free of oxidizing agent and use method of perm agent",
                    "一种不含氧化剂的烫发剂及其使用方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses an oxidant-free perm agent and a use method thereof. The perming agent comprises an agent A and an agent B, the agent A comprises a hair softening component, a hydrogen bond destroying agent and the like; and the agent B comprises a hair styling component and the like. According to the invention, cysteine and a hydrogen bond breaker are utilized to well break disulfide bonds in keratin under low-temperature, alkalescent and moist conditions to soften hair, and meanwhile, Michael reagent molecules containing an alpha-carbonyl carbon-carbon double bond group symmetrical structure are utilized to soften the hair in the absence of an oxidizing agent, so that the keratin can be effectively removed. Through a click reaction of a sulfydryl-Michael reagent, reconnection between sulfydryl groups is realized under a relatively low temperature condition. The method provided by the invention not only can shape the hair, but also can avoid the damage of oxidation to the hair, and has important significance for the health of the hair."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种不含氧化剂的烫发剂及其使用方法。本发明烫发剂包括剂A和剂B；剂A包括：头发软化组分、氢键破坏剂等；所述剂B包括：头发定型组分等。本发明利用半胱氨酸和氢键破坏剂在低温、弱碱性和湿润条件下很好地断开角蛋白中的二硫键，对头发进行软化，同时通过含有α‑羰基碳碳双键基团对称结构的迈克尔试剂分子，在没有氧化剂存在的情况下，通过巯基‑迈克尔试剂的点击反应，在较低温条件下实现巯基之间的重连。本发明所述方法既可以对头发塑型，又可以避免氧化对发丝的损伤，对于头发健康具有重要意义。"
                }
            ]
